Flight stats for Halong Bay - did you know?
Halong Bay is 81 mi from Noibai Airport (Hanoi, Vietnam).
Noibai Airport (Hanoi, Vietnam)
Right now, 34 airlines operate out of Noibai Airport.
Noibai Airport offers nonstop flights to 37 cities.
Every week, at least 1,511 domestic flights and 209 international flights depart from Noibai Airport.
